---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — WOA Cocktails"
  description="How WOA Cocktails collects, uses, and protects your information across our website and services in New York and Miami."
  styles={['woa-legal.css']}
>
  <main class="legal">
    <div class="legal-wrap">
      <div class="legal-head">
        <div class="eyebrow">— Legal</div>
        <h1 class="display">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: June 16, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-prose">
        <p class="lede">
          WOA Cocktails (&ldquo;WOA,&rdquo; &ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;)
          respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your
          information when you visit our website or inquire about our hospitality and beverage
          services.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information in two ways:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Information you provide.</strong> When you book a call, request a quote, or
            contact us, we collect details such as your name, email address, phone number, event
            information, and anything else you choose to share through our forms, scheduling tools,
            or by email.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Information collected automatically.</strong> When you browse the site, we may
            automatically collect device and usage information &mdash; such as your IP address,
            browser type, pages viewed, and referring links &mdash; through cookies and similar
            technologies.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to inquiries and prepare quotes;</li>
          <li>Schedule and coordinate events, consultations, and services;</li>
          <li>Operate, maintain, and improve our website;</li>
          <li>Send service-related communications;</li>
          <li>Measure and improve our marketing; and</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
        <p>
          We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience, serve personalized ads, and analyze
          our traffic. Cookies may be <strong>essential</strong> (required for the site to function),
          <strong>analytical</strong> (help us understand how the site is used), or
          <strong>advertising</strong> (used to deliver relevant marketing). You can manage your
          preferences through the cookie banner on our site or your browser settings. Disabling some
          cookies may affect how the site works.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We rely on trusted third-party providers to run our website and business, including
          scheduling (Calendly), forms (Tally), fonts (Google Fonts), hosting (Vercel), and social
          media platforms (Instagram and TikTok). These providers process information under their own
          privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h2>5. How We Share Information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with service providers
          who help us operate our business, when required by law, or in connection with a business
          transfer.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes
          described in this Policy, unless a longer retention period is required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on where you live, you may have the right to access, correct, delete, or restrict
          the use of your personal information, and to opt out of certain processing. To exercise
          these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:woacocktails@gmail.com">woacocktails@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission
          over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee
          absolute security.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our website is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal
          information from children.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a
          revised &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please reach out:</p>
        <div class="legal-contact">
          <strong>WOA Cocktails</strong><br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:woacocktails@gmail.com">woacocktails@gmail.com</a><br />
          New York &middot; Hector: <a href="tel:+16463386739">646-338-6739</a><br />
          Miami &middot; Fabio: <a href="tel:+12159390476">215-939-0476</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
